This is the readme for CHOICE


CHOICE is distributed under the terms of the GNU GPL.  See the file
'COPYING' for details.

Read the 'INSTALL' file to learn how to compile this program.

CHOICE supports program internationalization using the "Cats" library
for DOS.  ("Cats" is a UNIX catgets-like implementation.)  "Cats" is
distributed under the GNU LGPL and is available from
http://www.freedos.org/jhall/cats/
